//- views/index.pug
extends layout

block content
  .hero-main
    span.hero-kicker CHECKYOURTEACHING
    h1.hero-title Check your teaching and your class understanding.
    p.hero-subtitle
      | Turn each lesson into a simple quiz. Students answer, you see how much
      | they really understood and what to review next time.

    ul.hero-list
      li Upload your course (PDF/text) or create questions manually.
      li AI helps you generate multiple-choice questions in seconds.
      li Students join with a code and answer on any device.
      li At the end, they get the correction and you get a clear recap.

    .hero-actions
      a.btn-primary(href="/login?role=teacher") Teacher login
      a.btn-ghost(href="/login?role=student") Student login
